== Umwuga ==
Ariane Uwamahoro yatangiye itangazamakuru mu mwaka wa 2009 atangira uwo mwuga kuri radiyo Mariya [[Rwanda]] mu 2010 Ariane Uwamahoro nibwo yatangiye kwibanda ku makuru y'imikino. Aho yaje kuva kuri radiyo Mariya [[Rwanda]] akajya kuri radiyo Huguka, ahava ajya gukora mu kigo k'igihugu cy'itangazamakuru mu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] [https://www.rba.co.rw/ RBA]<ref>https://umuryango.rw/imyidagaduro/imikino/article/umunyamakuru-ariane-uwamahoro-yasezeranye-n-umukunzi-we-imbere-y-amategeko</ref>.

Ariane Uwamahoro umunyamakurukazi ukora itangazamakuru kandi wanaryize muri ishuri rikuru gaturika rya Kabgayi riherereye mu [[akarere ka Muhanga]] ([https://uck.ac.rw/ ICK]) aho yakuye impamyabumenyi y'icyiciro cya kabiri cya kaminuza mu itangazamakuru.<ref><nowiki>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/sports/who-are-top-female-sports-journalists-rwanda-meet-women-runningthe-show</nowiki></ref> <ref name=":0">https://www.linkedin.com/in/ariane-uwamahoro-911625171/?originalSubdomain=ca</ref> Ariane kandi yakomereje kwiga ibijyanye n'itangazamakuru mu gihugu cya kanada ( [https://www.acfas.ca/media/3191?gclid=CjwKCAjwjtOTBhAvEiwASG4bCIHv9n0FyGx0NV5QtdlyDE_wG6zVhBdBh26SNRkDJwsjMuirJP5FPBoCIU0QAvD_BwE Univerisit√© Laval] ) aho yakuye impamyabumenyi y'icyiciro cya gatatu cya kaminuza mu itangazamakuru ryambukiranya imipaka ( international journalism ).<ref name=":0" />

